Requirements
------------------------------------------
PHP 5.3 or higher


Getting started
-----------------------------------------

Note: The following example assumes that you put this in the index.php file and that both the library and the index.php file reside in the site root

// Sets the paths where the autoloader class will look for the classes
set_include_path(implode(PATH_SEPARATOR, array(
    get_include_path(),
    realpath(dirname(__FILE__) . '/SPL'),
)));

// We include the autoloader
require 'SPL/Autoload/Autoload.php';

// Namespace alias
use SPL\Autoload\Autoload as Autoload;

// Registering the autoloader
Autoload::register();


If you don't want the class to throw an Exception when no file for a class is found then also add the following line:

// Skips the Exception trigger when no file is found for the requested class
Autoload::skipException();


